query: Who had more FTEs in 2024, Apple or Tesla?
output:
Based on the information provided in the documents, Apple had more full-time equivalent employees (FTEs) than Tesla in 2024.

According to Apple's 2024 Form 10-K, Apple had approximately 164,000 full-time equivalent employees as of September 28, 2024.

According to Tesla's 2024 Form 10-K, Tesla had approximately 125,665 employee headcount worldwide as of December 31, 2024.

Therefore, Apple had approximately 38,335 more employees than Tesla in 2024.
